> Keep it compressed and actionable. Max ~100 lines.
>
> First-time setup: copy this file to `.agent/context.md` and start using it.
> Shared team truth lives in `PROGRESS.md`, the active plan/progress pair,
> `wiki/`, and `.agent/decisions.md` — all committed.

